---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — YKS" description="How we handle your data. Short, clear, and respectful." canonical="/privacy" noindex={false}>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 prose prose-invert text-sm">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <p>We collect minimal data. When you buy a guide, Lemon Squeezy handles payment and delivery. We receive your email for delivery and occasional important updates (you can opt out).</p>

    <p>Newsletter: We use Netlify Forms + a privacy-first ESP. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>

    <p>We do not sell data. We do not use creepy tracking. Plausible analytics is cookieless.</p>

    <p>For full details or data deletion requests, email hello@yks.example.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
